<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="sv">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>The Dadabaka Team</title>
<style>
  /* --- Grundläggande styling --- */
  body {
    margin: 0;
    font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0d0d0d, #111111);
    color: #fff;
    text-align: center;
  }

  header {
    background-color: #0f2027;
    padding: 40px 20px;
  }
  header h1 {
    color: #00ff88;
    font-size: 2.5em;
    margin: 0;
  }

  nav {
    margin-top: 15px;
  }
  nav a {
    color: #00aaff;
    text-decoration: none;
    margin: 0 10px;
    font-size: 1em;
  }

  section {
    padding: 40px 20px;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: auto;
  }
  h2 {
    color: #00ff88;
    margin-bottom: 15px;
    font-size: 1.8em;
  }
  p {
    font-size: 1em;
    line-height: 1.5em;
  }

  .button {
    display: inline-block;
    margin-top: 15px;
    padding: 10px 25px;
    background: #00aaff;
    color: #fff;
    text-decoration: none;
    border-radius: 6px;
    font-weight: bold;
  }

  footer {
    margin-top: 40px;
    padding: 20px;
    background-color: #0f2027;
    color: #888;
    font-size: 0.9em;
  }

  /* --- Responsiv mobilstil --- */
  @media (max-width: 500px) {
    header h1 { font-size: 2em; }
    nav a { display: block; margin: 5px 0; }
    h2 { font-size: 1.5em; }
    p { font-size: 0.95em; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
  <h1>The Dadabaka Team</h1>
  <nav>
    <a href="#home">Home</a>
    <a href="#rules">Rules</a>
    <a href="#server">Server</a>
    <a href="#bot">DadaCore</a>
  </nav>
</header>

<section id="home">
  <h2>Welcome!</h2>
  <p>Welcome to <strong>The Dadabaka Team</strong> – a friendly Minecraft & Discord community where you can chat, build, and have fun! Join our adventures and meet new friends.</p>
  <a href="https://discord.gg/hupDvMN2dq" class="button">Join our Discord</a>
</section>

<section id="rules">
  <h2>Server Rules</h2>
  <p>1️⃣ Be respectful to everyone.<br>
  2️⃣ No griefing or stealing.<br>
  3️⃣ No hacks, exploits, or bugs.<br>
  4️⃣ Keep spam and NSFW content out.<br>
  5️⃣ Follow staff instructions at all times.</p>
</section>

<section id="server">
  <h2>Server Info</h2>
  <p>Minecraft Server IP: <strong>mc.dadabaka.com</strong><br>
  Version: <strong>1.20</strong><br>
  PvP: <strong>Enabled</strong></p>
</section>

<section id="bot">
  <h2>DadaCore Bot</h2>
  <p>DadaCore is our official Discord bot for moderation, tickets, and fun commands. Keep the server safe and fun!</p>
</section>

<footer>
  &copy; 2026 The Dadabaka Team. All rights reserved.
</footer>

</body>
</html>